headline: HVAC and Water Systems Stocks Q2 Teardown: Carrier Global (NYSE:CARR) Vs The Rest
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at hvac and water systems stocks, starting with Carrier Global (NYSE:CARR).
